Kanye West - Runaway (My Beautiful Dark Twisted Fantasy bonus dvd)

Country : USA Genre : Hip-Hop Duration : 00:34:25 Year : 2010 Label : Roc-A-Fella, Def Jam Description : Runaway is A 35-minute long, short film directed by Kanye West. It serves as the music video for the song of the same name. It is inspired by other music-related films such as Purple Rain, Pink Floyd The Wall and Michael Jackson's Thriller and painters Picasso and Matisse. Directors Federico Fellini and Stanley Kubrick as well as fashion designer Karl Lagerfeld are also direct inspirations. 

The film depicts a romantic relationship between a man and a half-woman, half-phoenix, and is set to music by Kanye West, most of which is from his album My Beautiful Dark Twisted Fantasy (2010). 


